long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Inspired by bengrosser's Facebook Demetricator, Twitgnostic will remove identifying characteristics like usernames, avatars and handles from your Twitter timeline.

NEW TO VERSION 0.47: Some fixes for New(est) Twitter
NEW TO VERSION 0.46: This actually works again! (whoops!)
NEW TO VERSION 0.45: You can make non-reply tweets with extension on now 
NEW TO VERSION 0.42: Actually fixed masked-reply handling this time.
NEW TO VERSION 0.40: Improved masked reply handling, performance
NEW TO VERSION 0.31: Reply to Gnosticized tweets and have references to other users made legible to others!
NEW TO VERSION 0.25: Now toggled by clicking the "Gnosticon"!

This is a beta/prototype release, so please report any bugs/feature suggestions.
